  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents a single variation axis coordinate in a font's variation design space.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKFontVariationPositionCoordinate` associates a variation axis tag with a design-space value,
defining a single coordinate in a font's variation design space. Pass an array or span of these
coordinates to <xref:SkiaSharp.SKTypeface.Clone*> to produce a typeface with specific axis
settings.
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
